---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact — Skief Labs" description="Book a 30-minute discovery call. If the friction is real, it's worth a conversation.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="heading-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-navy-900 mb-8">
          If the friction is real, it's worth a conversation.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-10">
          Most teams reach out when something that used to work has stopped working at scale — and the manual workarounds are no longer sustainable. If that's where you are, this is the right next step.
        </p>
        <a href="#book" class="btn-primary">Book a 30-minute discovery call</a>
        <p class="text-navy-900/50 text-sm mt-3 italic">No pitch. No obligation. Just clarity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT THIS CONVERSATION IS -->
  <section class="section-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-linen">
            What this conversation is
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-linen text-xl font-serif italic">It's a diagnostic, not a demo.</p>
          <p>We won't walk you through our capabilities or show you what we've built for other people. We'll ask questions about your specific situation — how your business operates, where effort is concentrated, what's breaking — and tell you honestly whether we think we can help.</p>
          <p>Sometimes the answer is no. We're comfortable with that.</p>
          <p>Either way, you leave with a clearer picture of what's worth fixing — and what isn't.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO THIS CALL IS FOR -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div>
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-blue-500 mb-6">This conversation makes sense if you are</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
              <span>A founder, operator, or senior leader at a B2B company</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
              <span>Dealing with a real, recurring data or outbound problem</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
              <span>Looking for clarity, not a vendor pitch</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
              <span>Ready to invest in fixing the system, not just patching it</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900/40 mb-6">It's probably not worth your time if you are</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-navy-900/50 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-navy-900/30 mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
              <span>Running an RFP or comparing vendors on price</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-navy-900/30 mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
              <span>Looking for free consulting or a speculative proposal</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-navy-900/30 mt-1.5 text-xs">●</span>
              <span>Hoping for quick fixes over durable solutions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT HAPPENS AFTER -->
  <section class="section-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-linen mb-8">
          What happens after the call
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>If there's a fit, we'll outline a clear next step — either a scoped Data Intelligence build or a Sales Acceleration pilot, depending on where the problem lies.</p>
          <p>If there isn't a fit, we'll say so directly — and often point you toward something more useful.</p>
          <p>There's no obligation either way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CALENDLY / CTA -->
  <section id="book" class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="heading-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-navy-900 mb-8">
        Book your discovery call
      </h2>
      <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Choose a time that works for you. The call takes 30 minutes.
      </p>

      <!-- Calendly embed placeholder -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-navy-900/10 p-12 md:p-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        <p class="text-navy-900/40 text-sm mb-4">Calendly widget will be embedded here</p>
        <a href="https://calendly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary inline-block">
          Schedule on Calendly
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-navy-900/60 text-base">
        Or reach us directly: <a href="mailto:contact@skieflabs.com" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-200">contact@skieflabs.com</a>
      </p>
      <p class="text-navy-900/40 text-sm mt-8 italic font-serif">More business. Less busyness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
